==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Colewort
<hw>Cole"wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>cawlwyrt</ets>; <ets>cawl</ets> cole + <ets>wyrt</ets> wort. Cf.
<er>Collards</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A variety of cabbage in which
the leaves never form a compact head.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Any white cabbage before the head has become
firm.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Colfox</ent>⟦br⟧
